n6FcNvGm94bxDBDgkJUw-CQmBkhDDe90k9x2yQutIUSWhlGyiFTV_oX_QFFi4fK" rel=3D"" s=
tyle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">Great Online Game</a>.=
 Facebook, Microsoft, and other tech giants have committed to investing bil=
lions of dollars to build the Metaverse.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1=
a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Meanwhile, K-12 =
education in the United States has gotten <em>less </em>interesting. Educat=
ion policy has focused on shrinking the gap between the top and bottom stud=
ents, and the easiest way to do that is by putting a cap on the best-perfor=
ming students. Already, US students are <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substa=
ck.com/c/eJxFkE2OwyAMhU9Tdo34CS1ZsJjNXCNywElQA0TgzCi3H9osRrJsWU_2sz8HhEsup9=
1zJfZOI5072oS_dUMiLOyoWMbgrXhIo3Q_MG97L4w2LNRxLogRwmapHMj2Y9qCAwo5fSY4l5qt1=
